summary:
I prefer calling myself a hardworking and dedicated person. I strongly believe that for those who are determined the path of success would be straight and smooth. I am passionate about making the world more lively and real by implementing my classroom learnings into actual doings of mine. I like to travel, meet people and gain more experience each day. 

My interests lie in the domain of Consulting and Investment Banking though not restricted to these spheres alone.
